---
title: One-Pot Jambalaya-Inspired Tofu with Tomato RIce
description: Jambalaya is famous in New Orleans for the ability to pack serious smoky flavours into one colorful pot of rice. Our rendition is popping with green bell peppers, onions, garlic, tomato and tofu.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-jambalaya-inspired-tofu-0823a1dd.jpg
